# Dual Dialogue Test
Title: Dual Dialogue Test

## Dramatis Personae

BRICK - A retired man
STEEL - His partner
CHORUS - The ensemble

## ACT I

### SCENE 1

BRICK
Screw retirement.

STEEL ^
Screw retirement.

### SCENE 2

